Title: Curvature flows in semi-Riemannian manifolds
Authors: Claus Gerhardt
Categories: math.DG
Comments: 48 pages, v4: minor typos corrected, this version will be published
MSC-class: 35J60, 53C21, 53C44, 53C50, 58J05
Journal-ref: Geometric Flows (Huai-Dong Cao and Shing-Tung Yau, eds.), Surveys
  in Differential Geometry, vol. XII, International Press of Boston,
  Somerville, MA, 2008, pp. 113--165
\\
  We prove that the limit hypersurfaces of converging curvature flows are
stable, if the initial velocity has a weak sign, and give a survey of the
existence and regularity results.
